channel.title: [562] how do you change the text in the quest tab? [562]
channel.description:
I looked up everywhere online, and people are getting the same anwser from everybody else, "I know how to do it, but im not gonna tell you." Can someone please friggin release the public information on how to change the text in the quest tab for 562. Almost everyone in moparscape would probably ++Rep++ you, and i don't know what else, but you probably would be famous. Lol IDK, but could someone just please release it because im sick and tired of these greedy people that wont release it thank you! :D
[center] :confused: Well deven tried to help but we got no where so anyone else want to help me? :confused:[/center]
[center]:( If you don't feel like releasing it then could you just please private message me it then :([/center]
